Sentencas: This study demonstrated the feasibility of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) operating on fuels gasified from a carbon-bed containing a renewable biomass.
Titulo: Study of a renewable biomass fueled SOFC: The effect of catalysts

Sentencas: Coconut shell carbon was used as the renewable biomass for the gasification to power the SOFC at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Study of a renewable biomass fueled SOFC: The effect of catalysts

Sentencas: The study was particularly focused on the effect of catalysts on the efficiency of the gasification process, thus the performance of tubular SOFC powered by these gasified fuels.
Titulo: Study of a renewable biomass fueled SOFC: The effect of catalysts

Sentencas: SOFCs with catalysts such as Fe2O3 and K2CO3 added coconut shell carbon showed higher power density compared to that without catalyst.
Titulo: Study of a renewable biomass fueled SOFC: The effect of catalysts

Sentencas: The improved cell performance can be ascribed to a promoted carbon conversion rate by the catalysts, and consequently higher concentration of gaseous fuels.
Titulo: Study of a renewable biomass fueled SOFC: The effect of catalysts
